# NPM Automation Token
# Used by the `npm run release:patch` pipeline to publish the virgo-mcp standalone package headlessly.
#
# Instructions to get this token:
# 1. Log in to https://www.npmjs.com/
# 2. Click your profile picture -> Access Tokens
# 3. Click "Generate New Token" -> "Classic Token"
# 4. Name it "Virgo Agent Publisher" and select "Automation" type.
# 5. Click Generate and paste the token below.

NPM_TOKEN=npm_...
